com.avaya.jtapi.tsapi

Interface LucentEndpointRegisteredEvent

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AddressEvent, Event, LucentEndpointEvent

    public interface LucentEndpointRegisteredEvent
extends LucentEndpointEvent
    This private event is used to indicate that an endpoint has registered to a station which was being monitored using a LucentV11AddressListener. It provides information about the endpoint, which is provided by V11RegisteredEndpointInfo.
    See Also:
    LucentV11AddressListener, V11RegisteredEndpointInfo
